[u][b]Controls:[/b][/u]
[b]W/A/S/D[/b]   - Move your character
[b]E[/b] - Enter area when prompted
[b]Q[/b] - Exit panel/area when prompted

[u][b]Inventory[/b][/u]
[b]Left Click[/b] - Pick up/drop entire stack of items
[b]Right Click[/b] - Pick up/drop half of stack
[b]CTRL+Left Click[/b] - Move entire stack into free spot
[b]Scoop Left Click[/b] - Pick up single solid ingredient
[b]Scoop Right Click[/b] - Drop single solid ingredient
[b]Flagon Left Click[/b] - Pick up pint of liquid ingredient
[b]Flagon Right Click[/b] - Drop pint of liquid ingredient

