text = "You are a hermit that forages ingredients from a number of biomes, cooks them following recipes and sells the product in town.

Click on the paper at the bottom of the screen to bring up notes and recipes for more information.

Controls:
W/A/S/D   - Move your character
E - Enter area when prompted
Q - Exit panel/area when prompted

Inventory
Left Click - Pick up/drop entire stack of items
Right Click - Pick up/drop half of stack
CTRL+Left Click - Move entire stack into free spot
Scoop Left Click - Pick up single solid ingredient
Scoop Right Click - Drop single solid ingredient
Flagon Left Click - Pick up pint of liquid ingredient
Flagon Right Click - Drop pint of liquid ingredient

Use the flagon to measure individual pints from your inventory to the cauldron.  Add ingredients according to the recipe and add wood to the cauldron to control the temperature.  When the recipe is in progress, the water will change colours, then eventually your products will appear.

Some ingredients need to be processed at the prep table to the left of the cauldron."
